Package: yolor
Type: Package
Title: YOLO Object Detection from ShinyLabel Annotations
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Lalit", "GIS", email = "your@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R-native interface for YOLO object detection that integrates
    directly with ShinyLabel annotation exports. Provides functions to read
    ShinyLabel SQLite databases and CSV exports, manage YOLO-format datasets,
    run inference using YOLO models via reticulate (Ultralytics), compute
    comprehensive accuracy metrics (mAP, precision, recall, F1, AP per class,
    confusion matrix, PR curves, F1-confidence curves), visualise all metrics,
    and export results to CSV, JSON, PNG, and HTML reports.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
